review_text: One of the best Trail Parks in Montreal.

Amazing park. You can find an amalgamation of forest, Park, hiking, big river and an awesome view of the city. If you are planning to spend your whole day together with your family, friends and kids don’t miss it. You won’t know how time flies when you get in the river view podium. Slightly blowing cool air, fantastique river views after a bit of tiredness of forest walk OMG...... amazing. I don’t have words to explain........ just can say go and get experience
I like this park, it has great views..❤

(Translated by Google) Nature oasis in the heart of the city. Varied flora and fauna. Many spaces are picnics. Trails and cycle path. Site of historical value. The view of the river contributes to the feeling of being out of touch.

(Original)
Oasis de nature au cœur de la ville. Faune et flore variée. Nombreux espaces se picnics. Sentiers et piste cyclable. Emplacement à valeur historique. La vue sur la rivière contribue au sentiment de décrochement.
